rComments: This isn't a very easy class but Vincent is a great friendly professor, Lots of readings! Pop quizzes every week or so, 2 tests. And 4 papers. Great professor!

Take notes in his class. He teaches English but he really appreciates the context in which novels are written so at times his class seems more like a history class. However, all the historical background he provides is totally relevant to the novels and deepens your understanding. I hate history, but he presented it really well. P.S. He's a looker!
